 />\n推到佢地收皮</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n藝人孔德賢與落選港姐廖慧儀拍拖傳聞甚囂塵上，最近分別上載屋內整嘢食的相片，被踢爆一齊玩煮飯仔，及後男方見成為熱話即刪相。今晚孔德賢出席《big big shop新春感謝祭》活動時，否認雙方發展地下情，他說：「嗰晚係有個共同朋友嘅生日派對，我上到去先至知佢喺度，但都冇乜特別交流，過去就由得佢過去，都係食餐飯。如果<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">我有嘢唔會白癡到咁樣Po相，刪相係因為我一次過上載5張，覺得太煩，所以先至精簡一啲（依家冇聯絡？）冇聯絡，</span></strong></span></span>亦冇一齊合作過，我仲係拍緊嘢（之後會避忌啲？）會，會問清楚有啲乜人先。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HewAgv2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHewAgv2.png&h=7961634e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JtRsR4o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJtRsR4o.png&h=b1970263&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n，<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xBkdNEP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxBkdNEP.jpg&h=a9c4926a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"608c31a7e4dcfc847304a69c046aecf097783556","tid":2375311,"uid":167658,"like":43,"dislike":4,"score":39,"quote":{"pid":"8f6bca5e34783c9a0d5fc750db73a7fc87d4d00b","tid":2375311,"uid":79563,"like":11,"dislike":113,"score":-102,"quote":{"pid":"66e2b0c5224cb982b76d1c7237528f648e3fa63f","tid":2375311,"uid":4826,"like":170,"dislike":4,"score":166,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T03:10:25.000Z","msg":"為一條冇波嘅女犧牲真係好傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T03:25:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ezp2kEU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fezp2kEU.png&h=547e7064&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bLq80ES.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbLq80ES.png&h=68be8885&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T10:57:50.000Z","msg":"D膚色好核突<br />\n一定黑Lin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/